"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-tamara-potocka-collapses-poolside-womens-race-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News  August 2, 2024 / 7:49 AM EDT/ CBS/AP  Slovakia swimmer Tamara Potocka collapsed poolside Friday morning after a qualifying heat of the women's 200-meter individual medley at theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9999391198115938, \"rank\": 6.088379668463767e-05, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 49, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"score\": 0.9726988096403459, \"rank\": 0.02569819402050412, \"text\": \"CBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\"}, {\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999947877888056, \"rank\": 4.9270613886938e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9807407729724158, \"rank\": 0.019222715263880114, \"text\": \"Slovakia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was given first aid and then carried off on a stretcher.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka, 21, was seen wearing an oxygen mask as she was taken away for medical attention.\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medical personal at the pool said she was conscious.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Slovakian teamtold BBC Sportthat Potocka is an asthmatic and had an asthma attack.\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.7750073240996478, \"rank\": 0.2797370874788838, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 452, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka collapsed as she got out of the water and almost immediately was surrounded by a half-dozen medical attendants who put her on a stretcher after about a minute and carried her off the pool deck.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka was able to communicate with doctors and she was taken to hospital for further medical supervision, the BBC reported.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.7750073240996478, \"rank\": 0.2797370874788838, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not clear if she received CPR.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Israeli swimmer Lea Polonsky, who swam two heats after Potocka, said swimmers know their sport has inherent risks.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 0.8287888175144409, \"rank\": 0.19235314155548788, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Polonsky\", \"score\": 0.9999968328518339, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lea Polonsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Polonsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Polonsky\"}, {\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course that's something in the back of your mind, but we do every day push ourselves to the limit,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You always know something like that can happen.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something you think about during the race, but it's always there.\\\"\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is Potocka's first Olympics.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She resides in the Slovakian capital of Bratislava.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bratislava\", \"score\": 0.9999999713700167, \"rank\": 2.853460409500995e-08, \"text\": \"Bratislava\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bratislava\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bratislava\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka finished seventh in her heat in a time of 2 minutes, 14.20 seconds.\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her time was not fast enough to advance her to the semifinals of the event, which eliminated her from the competition.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1519, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, or redistributed.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1657, \"title\"